  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Cache
    This interface represents the cache which stores data after making a api call to reduce API calls.
    FlexiblePortfolio
    This interface represents the operations on a single Flexible portfolio.
    FlexibleStock
    This interface represents the operations that can be performed on a single stock of a company in flexible portfolio.
    FlexibleStocksList
    This interface represents the operations that can be performed on a stock list of a company in flexible portfolio purchased on different dates.
    Model
    This interface represents a model.
    NewModel
    This interface represents a NewModel which extends previously used Model interface.
    User
    This interface represents operations that a user can perform.
